iner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brittney Griner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\"}, {\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewell_Loyd\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jewell Loyd\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewell_Loyd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jewell_Loyd\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Atkins is the only one of those returnees - other than Griner, who has extenuating circumstances, and is another lock to suit up in red, white and blue if she so chooses - whose play has declined since the last Olympiad, but considering she also played for the USA during the 2022 FIBA World Cup, Atkins will likely be prioritized by the committee.\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Griner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittney_Griner\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, her status as a 2024 Olympian is probably the most tenuous of these eight players.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2464, \"end\": 2472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998390390049, \"rank\": 1.609610708253282e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  That leaves at most five, and likely four, spots for new blood, and the competition is fierce.Kahleah Copper,Sabrina Ionescu, Betnijah Laney,Kelsey PlumandAlyssa Thomaswere all additionally part of the World Cup squad.\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2644, \"end\": 2650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahleah_Copper\", \"score\": 0.9997739198211011, \"rank\": 0.00022613103351990183, \"text\": \"Copper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahleah_Copper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahleah_Copper\"}, {\"begin\": 2644, \"end\": 2650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahleah_Copper\", \"score\": 0.9997739198211011, \"rank\": 0.00022613103351990183, \"text\": \"Copper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahleah_Copper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kahleah_Copper\"}, {\"begin\": 2651, \"end\": 2666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sabrina Ionescu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\"}, {\"begin\": 2651, \"end\": 2666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sabrina Ionescu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\"}, {\"begin\": 2668, \"end\": 2682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betnijah_Laney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Betnijah Laney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betnijah_Laney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betnijah_Laney\"}, {\"begin\": 2668, \"end\": 2682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betnijah_Laney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Betnijah Laney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betnijah_Laney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Betnijah_Laney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ionescu averaged the fewest minutes in Australia, but she, Thomas and Plum all have been All-WNBA selections within the past two seasons, with the latter two finishing top-five in MVP voting.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2800, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9998616590226643, \"rank\": 0.00013258129758260788, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2820, \"end\": 2826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isiah_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9743384796700054, \"rank\": 0.025307999497181693, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isiah_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isiah_Thomas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plum's history withthe three-on-three teamshould also give her a leg up with the committee, which brings us to her fellow gold medalists in that sport's debut in 2021:Allisha GrayandJackie Young.\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 3144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both players seem too good to be left off of the roster, especially Young, but that is always the case with the American national team.\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3261, \"end\": 3283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9996419653006241, \"rank\": 0.0003576563801944503, \"text\": \"American national team\", \"types\": [