he end of the roster and then grow into the future leaders.\", \"from\": 4381, \"to\": 4476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wilson has talked about learning from Taurasi and Sue Bird how to set the standard, which she put into practice along with Stewart at the last World Cup.\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4481, \"end\": 4487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.693041472970881e-34, \"text\": \"Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A'ja_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 4519, \"end\": 4526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.412628853046436e-65, \"text\": \"Taurasi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana_Taurasi\"}, {\"begin\": 4531, \"end\": 4539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sue_Bird\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sue Bird\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sue_Bird\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sue_Bird\"}, {\"begin\": 4604, \"end\": 4611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2792873845983994e-56, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breanna_Stewart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would make sense for Clark to be the latest ing\\u00e9nue to take her place as Team USA's 12th player, but with the 2004 No.\", \"from\": 4632, \"to\": 4753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4712, \"end\": 4720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999859574949446, \"rank\": 1.398770313635295e-05, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1 pick Taurasi still kicking, there may not be enough space.\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps the committee will take solace in Boston representing the current generation, while a cohort of older guards compete in the backcourt.\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4861, \"end\": 4867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\", \"score\": 0.9999999992219273, \"rank\": 6.437756973825569e-10, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deciding between Atkins, Copper, Allisha Gray, Ionescu, Ogunbowale, Plum and Young for what figures to be three spots will be difficult enough without adding Clark to the mix.\", \"from\": 4958, \"to\": 5133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4995, \"end\": 5007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allisha_Gray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Allisha Gray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allisha_Gray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allisha_Gray\"}, {\"begin\": 5009, \"end\": 5016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.141282126269425e-48, \"text\": \"Ionescu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Ionescu\"}, {\"begin\": 5009, \"end\": 5016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.