pedia.org/resource/USA_Basketball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are the biggest showcase of women's basketball worldwide.\", \"from\": 5362, \"to\": 5432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A player like Clark belongs on that stage if the selection committee wants to build off the momentum the sport is generating stateside.\", \"from\": 5433, \"to\": 5568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  There will be plenty of superstars on the national team whether Clark makes the cut or not.\", \"from\": 5570, \"to\": 5676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the U.S. will be prohibitive favorites regardless of what combination of these players suits up in Paris.\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5784, \"end\": 5789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.3197570505636718e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The specific composition of this roster, however, will reveal what the committee prioritizes, be it national team history, domestic success, balance of youth/veterans or the most marketable names.\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All of those possibilities are on the table.\", \"from\": 5984, \"to\": 6028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo of Caitlin Clark: Marc Piscotty / Icon Sportswire via Getty Images)  Spot the pattern.\", \"from\": 6030, \"to\": 6123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6044, \"end\": 6057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caitlin Clark\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Clark\"}, {\"begin\": 6044, \"end\": 6057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caitlin_Cla